  "description": {
    "S": "The slow cooker does all the work with this easy, flavorful, and healthy crockpot white chicken chili. Creamy, comforting, and loaded with tender shredded chicken and hearty beans in a smoky salsa verde broth finished with cream cheese and fresh lime."
  },
